properties.Name: IncidentPartyInjury
properties.Description: The incident injury(s) incurred by the associated party. Note: This may not be the opinion of a medical professional.

Columns.Name: IncidentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Incident.

Columns.Name: InjuredPartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.

Columns.Name: InjuryTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an injury type.

Columns.Name: FatalInjuryIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates the injury resulted in a fatality.

Columns.Name: FirstAidIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether first aid was applied at the location of the incident. First aid in this use does not apply to third party medical attention such as that provided by a medical professional.

Columns.Name: MedicalAttentionRequiredIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether medical attention by a third party medical professional was required.

Columns.Name: NumberOfMissedWorkDays
Columns.Description: The number of work days missed as a result of the injury sustained as a result of the incident.

Columns.Name: IncidentPartyInjuryNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding an incident party injury.

Columns.Name: BodyPartId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a body part.
